        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;This resolution condemns the use of congressionally directed spending, community project funding, and other earmarks to direct federal funding. It also affirms the need to address inflation by curbing federal spending.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
